As an administrator of the online shop
I want to edit content without deep knowledge of frontend 
So that I can increase the income of the online shop 

Scope

CRM functionality 
Account of the online shop administrator
Ability to edit content



Precondition:

CRM functionality is implemented
The Administrator is logged in 

Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1: The administrator of the online shop can edit content without deep knowledge of frontend 
Given: The administrator is logged in 
When: Click on the "Edit content" buttons 
And: Edit content
And: click the "Save" button
Then: The page content is changed





